Odaily Planet Daily News: Important events and data forecasts for next week: Super Central Bank Week, US retail data
1. Monday: China's May total retail sales and industrial added value annual rate, US June New York Fed manufacturing index;
2. Tuesday: US May retail sales monthly rate, import price index monthly rate and industrial output monthly rate; US Senate votes on GENIUS Act;
3. Wednesday: US initial jobless claims;
4. Thursday: The Federal Reserve, Swiss National Bank, and Bank of England announce interest rate decisions, and US stocks are closed for one day;
5. Friday: US June Philadelphia Fed manufacturing index. (Jinshi)
